room_title: Escape room "Stewie's Bedroom" by The Door Escape Room in Charlotte
review: We were blessed to be able to spend our Thanksgiving holiday together my daughter chose this place . I was unsure never did anything like this omg what a blast so much fun we all laughed had a good time give this a try with family or friends if you never did something like this or just bored and need something different to do go for it,
